        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com/email/images/syria-sanctions-lift-reconstruction-opportunity.jpg" alt="With the lifting of this major obstacle to economic recovery, the long-awaited doors are opening for reconstruction and development" href="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com" />
        <mj-text padding="0px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#A9A7AF">
          <p style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.2; color: #A9A7AF;"><i>
